      "content": "interesting. so u think the whole thing was basically a mistake? i mean, some people argue that removing a dictator who was potentially a massive threat to regional stability and human rights was a win in itself, even if things got messy later. wouldn't u say there was a clear benefit to getting rid of Gaddafi?",
